casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Walker.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Walker (1988), 40 Ohio St. 3d 604.]

(No. D.R. 88-8 Submitted November 15, 1988 Decided December 14, 1988.)

The resignation of Thomas B. Walker as an attorney is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Locher, Holmes, Douglas, Wright and H. Brown, JJ., concur.
